## Contributing

Contributions are welcome!

* Add new tools by creating a new module in `cloud_tools/` with a `Typer` app.
* Register the module in `cli.py` with:

```python
app.add_typer(new_tool.app, name="new-tool")
```

* Write unit tests in `tests/`.
* Follow code formatting standards (e.g., `black`, `flake8`).

